# M3.23 update: cheapcode_auto_3_axis_dominance_on_multistep_over_raw_frontier
# REMOVED from this assume-clause — it was empirically FALSIFIED in
# M3.11/M3.11b (compound wrapper FAIL on cost+latency 1.3-1.9× / 5×). The
# falsified claim is preserved at line 172 with confidence 0.05 and obs flag
# flipped to True per atom 0013 (calibration-as-credential disclosure: failed
# experiments stay visible). The smart-axis substitution (voter, M3.18-M3.20)
# is captured at SECTION Y; v1 ships discharge cites it. v2 here reflects the
# residual structural claim: surgical architecture inherits cheapllm receipts
# WITHOUT staking on the failed wrapper-3-axis-dominance.
theorem cheapcode_v2_is_surgical_and_inherits_cheapllm_receipts
  assume cheap_tier_uses_deepseek_v4_flash and cheap_fast_uses_race_k_cheapllm_strategy and smart_tier_routes_directly_to_capable_model and long_context_uses_grok_4_fast and auto_wrapper_apophatic_routing_works and verifier_hook_catches_50pct_of_wrong_answers and cross_witness_pattern_lifts_hard_reasoning and plan_decompose_amortizes_smart_calls and best_of_k_3_lifts_completion_5_to_15pct and cross_model_verification_lifts_over_self_verify and parallel_leaf_execution_keeps_latency_below_raw and honest_niche_dominance_includes_cost_adjusted_hard_reasoning and provider_registry_propagation_holds and or_provider_inheritance_safe and surgical_fork_loc_budget_holds and upstream_files_modified_within_budget and weekly_rebase_holds and cheapllm_receipts_anchor and cheapllm_context_anchor and iai_router_pattern_anchor and transfer_overstated_anchor and mizaj_substrate_anchor and khatim_negative_knowledge_anchor
  proves True
  by audit cheapcode-v2-surgical-architecture-post-wrapper-falsification-m3-23

# Intermediate claim - burhan can only cite theorems from claim cells,
# not from another theorem's assumption directly. This claim materializes
# the surgical-architecture theorem's verdict for re-citation.
claim cheapcode_v2_surgical_architecture_audited: Bool @>=0.85 = cite cheapcode_v2_is_surgical_and_inherits_cheapllm_receipts

theorem cheapcode_v2_outperforms_named_alternatives
  assume cheapcode_v2_surgical_architecture_audited and cheapcode_beats_codex_after_pricing_fetch and cheapcode_beats_vanilla_opencode_via_routing
  proves True
  by audit competitive-scorecard

